# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo. Working copies are checked
# out with LF on every platform; commits store LF. This keeps diffs free of
# whole-file CRLF rewrites.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary types — never touch.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.bmp binary
*.svg binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.jar binary
*.keystore binary
*.jks binary
*.dex binary
